, KG Luijkx, HR Boeije, HJM Vrijhoef; citation_volume=83; citation_issue=4; citation_publication_date=2014; citation_pages=235-248; citation_doi=10.1016/j.ijmedinf.2014.01.004; citation_id=CR26\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_journal_title=Disabil. Rehabil. Assist. Technol.; citation_title=Technology and active agency of older adults living in service house environment; citation_author=M Sallinen, O Hentonen, A Karki; citation_volume=10; citation_issue=1; citation_publication_date=2015; citation_pages=27-31; citation_doi=10.3109/17483107.2013.836685; citation_id=CR27\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_journal_title=BMC. Health Serv. Res.; citation_title=Exploring barriers to participation and adoption of telehealth and telecare within the Whole System Demonstrator trial: a qualitative study; citation_author=C Sanders, A Rogers, R Bowen, P Bower, S Hirani, M Cartwright; citation_volume=12; citation_publication_date=2012; citation_pages=220; citation_doi=10.1186/1472-6963-12-220; citation_id=CR28\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_journal_title=Interactions; citation_title=From designing to co-designing to collective dreaming: three slices in time; citation_author=L Sanders, PJ Stappers; citation_volume=21; citation_issue=6; citation_publication_date=2014; citation_pages=24-33; citation_doi=10.1145/2670616; citation_id=CR29\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_title=Ein dreiviertel Jahr mit PAUL: Assisted Living in Kaiserslautern; citation_publication_date=2009; citation_id=CR30; citation_author=A Spellerberg; citation_author=L Schelisch; citation_publisher=VDE\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_title=Gerotranscendence: A Developmental Theory of Positive Aging; citation_publication_date=2005; citation_id=CR31; citation_author=L Tornstam; citation_publisher=Springer\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"UN Un